<%# Founding-50 welcome email — fires automatically on every signup via the
    Clerk webhook. The "first 50" copy is accurate while signups < 50; revise
    this and the subject in clerk-webhook.ts once the founding cohort fills. %>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Welcome to OTP</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f5f5f7;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#1a1a1a;line-height:1.6;">
  <div style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;padding:40px 24px;">

    <div style="text-align:left;margin-bottom:28px;">
      <div style="display:inline-block;padding:6px 12px;background:#0f766e;color:white;border-radius:6px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;">OTP</div>
    </div>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">Hi <%= firstName && String(firstName).trim() ? firstName : 'there' %>,</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">I'm David. I built OTP, and you just signed up, which makes you one of the first 50 people on it. The founding 50 get every tool free for life, and you get a direct line to me.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">I'd like to give you that line right now. Grab 20 minutes with me:</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0;">
      <a href="https://calendly.com/davidsteel/otp-intro" style="display:inline-block;padding:11px 22px;background:#0f766e;color:#ffffff;border-radius:8px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;">Book 20 minutes with me</a>
    </p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:16px;">I'll walk you through OTP, help you get your own chart set up, and hear what made you sign up. You're early enough that what you tell me changes the product.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 28px 0;font-size:16px;">Glad you're here.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 32px 0;font-size:16px;">David</p>

    <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:32px 0;">

    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#777;margin:0 0 8px 0;">
      You're receiving this because you signed up at orgtp.com.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#777;margin:0;">
      <a href="<%- locals.unsubUrl || ('https://orgtp.com/api/v1/newsletter/unsubscribe/' + encodeURIComponent(email)) %>" style="color:#777;">Unsubscribe</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
